race.comment: LOCO STORM (2) finished sixth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 320m at this track, taking a Maiden in a solid 18.19. Expected to push the clock again here. LOCO BOOM (4) was in the placings last time but prior to that clocked a speedy 22.79 win over 401m at this track. Expected to feature on best figures. PEPE MORADA (1) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Black Myth Wave (32.55) in a Grade 5. The form from her last run stacks up well. Should be thereabouts. MISSILE BOY (7) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to turn the form around.
